OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFacebook-owner Meta to cut 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F13% of its workforce       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Meta, which owns Facebook, Instagram   
OL,6, and WhatsApp, has announced that it    
OL,7, will cut 13% of its workforce.         
OL,9,FThe first mass lay-offs in the firm's  
OL,10,Fhistory will result in 11,000          
OL,11,Femployees, from a worldwide headcount  
OL,12,Fof 87,000, losing their jobs.          
OL,14,FMeta chief executive Mark Zuckerberg   
OL,15,Fsaid the cuts were "the most difficult 
OL,16,Fchanges we've made in Meta's history". 
OL,18,FThe news follows major lay-offs at     
OL,19,FTwitter, which cut about half its      
OL,20,Fstaff, and other tech firms.           
